0. Copy the directory in Linux system

1. Add path to .bashrc file
export PATH=$PATH:/userhome/where_Auxiliary

2. Alter the executive persmision in Auxiliary directory
chmod +x ./*

3. Use it in VASP running path, like `check_force`
Input:
[Ipiro@HPC vasp_opt]$check_force
Output
============================
    EDIFFG: -1e-05 (eV/Å²)
----------------------------
